<p>If your tree is beyond redemption or if it poses risk to the surrounding structures or people, a tree removal is mandated. A tree removal is a high-risk task that ought to be left to the pros.</p>
<p>Is the tree on your property hazardous or do you need help clearing room for a new structure? We are here to help. At Al Miley & Associates, we work with a team of experienced and highly skilled arborists in Oakville to diagnose the condition of trees and recommend the best treatment. Call us now for a free quote</p>[/x_text][/x_column][x_column bg_color="" type="1/2"  style="padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px; "][x_custom_headline level="h2" looks_like="h3" accent="false"]Tree Protection Oakville[/x_custom_headline][x_gap size="30px"][x_text class="left-text "]To be healthy, trees require good care and the right person monitoring and administering treatment when they have health issues. There are innumerable pests and diseases that affect plants. The good news is that most of these problems can be treated regardless of how serious they seem to be. Our arborists have even restored trees that seemed dead.

