Al Miley &amp; Associates guarantees tailored approach to tree care. When it comes to tree protection, we donâ€™t just treat the symptoms. We dig deeper to understand the effects of the local weather, regional pests and diseases and the landscape. Treatment is selected once we are certain of what we are dealing with.[/x_text][/x_column][/x_row][/x_section][x_section bg_color="#f7f9d2" id="section-services" class="center-text " style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px; padding: 70px 0px 70px 0px; "][x_row inner_container="true" marginless_columns="false" bg_color="" style="margin: 0px auto 0px auto; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; "][x_column bg_color="" type="1/2"  style="padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px; "][x_custom_headline level="h2" looks_like="h3" accent="false"]Tree Pruning Oakville[/x_custom_headline][x_gap size="30px"][x_text class="left-text "]<p>Regular pruning is needed to keep trees and shrubs healthy and looking flawless. Pruning can boost the aesthetics of your yard while at the same time offering a range of undeniable benefits. Here are the three benefits you can count on.</p>
<h4>Health</h4>
<p>Pruning involves the removal of weak, damaged and excess plant parts. This will improve air circulation around the plant while at the same time improving sunlight penetration. Pruning will also reduce the risk of pest infections and give the plant a better chance to fight diseases. A healthy plant will live longer.Â </p><h4>Safety</h4>
<p>Dead, broken or weak tree parts can fall off and cause accidents and damage to structures. The removal of the hazardous tree limbs will reduce the risk of damage or accidents. Our in-house team has the equipment and skills needed to assess and ensure a tree has no hazardous parts.</p>
<h4>Manicured landscape</h4>
<p>A professionally pruned tree will look great and subsequently boost the aesthetics of your property. Companies can also benefit from the service by improving their brand image with an amazing landscape. A well-maintained landscape will radiate a positive atmosphere. Our expert team of certified arborists in Oakville will transform your yard into something you can admire.</p>[/x_text][/x_column][x_column bg_color="" type="1/2"  style="padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px; "][x_custom_headline level="h2" looks_like="h3" accent="false"]Tree Arborists Oakville[/x_custom_headline][x_gap size="30px"][x_text class="left-text "]<p>A manicured landscape calls for professional tree and shrub trimming. At Miley & Associates, we believe that trimming is something that should be considered regularly to achieve a visually captivating landscape. We have tailored a range of professional services with the aim of creating pristine landscapes. Our services include but are not limited to storm cleanup, tree cutting, stump removal and trimming. We are known for our attention to detail in creating aesthetic yards.</p>
<p>Benefits of our trimming services</p>
<h4>Safety</h4>
<p>Human activities, gusts of wind and a range of other factors can cause broken or weak tree limbs. These can be hazardous if they fall. Safety has always been a top priority in yard maintenance. We will inspect your trees and ensure all hazardous parts are taken care of.</p>
<h4>Development</h4>
<p>Trees will not heal as fast if they have weak, broken, dead or diseased limbs on them. Our work as certified arborists is to remove these parts to enhance air circulation and sunlight penetration. Doing this helps the tree to heal itself faster.</p>
<h4>Aesthetics</h4>
<p>Creating for you a landscape that is bright and worth admiration is what we do with professionally shaped trees and shrubs. We are known for our keen eye in the creation of harmonious designs.</p>
